## Technical Accuracy Requirements

### Cost Estimates
- Sonnet 4.5: $3 input / $15 output per million tokens
- Opus 4: $15 input / $75 output per million tokens
- Typical task: 10,000-30,000 tokens
- MVP project: $200-$500

**Always include:**
- Token estimate
- Cost range
- Timeline estimate

### Model References
- Current: Claude Sonnet 4.5, Claude Opus 4
- Model IDs: claude-sonnet-4-20250514, claude-opus-4-20250514
- Mention extended thinking explicitly
- Context window: 200k tokens

### Tool References
- Cline (VS Code extension)
- Claude Code (terminal tool)
- Claude web interface (claude.ai)

**Be specific about versions and features.**

